Hangman Game ðŸŽ¯

A simple Python implementation of the classic Hangman game.
Guess the hidden word letter by letter before you run out of attempts!

 Features

Randomly selects a word from a predefined list

Tracks guessed letters

Displays the word with blanks (_) for unguessed letters

Ends when the player either guesses all letters or runs out of attempts

How to Run

Make sure you have Python 3 installed.

Save the code as hangman.py.

Open a terminal or command prompt and run:

python hangman.py